{"title":"Python入门_1","uid":"ba74248c7926adca0e0698f53d200e9f","slug":"python_1","date":"2023-07-16T06:23:13.146Z","updated":"2023-07-16T07:37:03.038Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/python_1.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/07/16/08EXtiiS.jpg","content":"<p>已经下载好了python？很好……我们可以开始了！</p>\n<h1 id=\"Hello-World\"><a href=\"#Hello-World\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hello World\"></a>Hello World</h1><p><del>我猜你应该还没忘掉print吧（</del><br>首先，要写一段可以重复运行的python程序，需要你打开IDLE，选择Flie-&gt;New File<br><img src=\"/../pictrues/python_1.1.png\"></p>\n<p>然后你会看到<strong>这个</strong>：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../pictrues/python_1.2.png\" alt=\"死去的微机课知识\"></p>\n<p>OK，现在可以试着输入一些代码了……</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Hello World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Another one\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>代码中的’()’以及’”‘都要用英文输入法</p>\n</div>\n<p>然后……按下F5</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../pictrues/python_1.3.png\" alt=\"文件必须要保存，按下OK来保存\"></p>\n<p>按下OK，然后选个位置写个名字……就叫demo吧（</p>\n<p>如果没什么问题，结果是这样子的：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../pictrues/python_1.4.png\" alt=\"你好！\"></p>\n<p>这就是第一个程序了~输出了两条结果。而且，可以看出来，程序是从上到下执行的，而且只执行一次。</p>\n<h1 id=\"Print\"><a href=\"#Print\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Print()\"></a>Print()</h1><p>介绍……print() 函数！</p>\n<p>这里的<strong>函数</strong>……要<strong>感性</strong>的理解一下……<del>我不会讲,反正理解成命令就好了</del></p>\n<p>总之，python在执行这个函数时，会输出’()’里边的东西。这个“东西”，成分可以很复杂（</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\">#嘘……我是注释</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#在这里写的东西不会对程序有半点影响</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#啊哈，要不要猜一下下面输出的结果？</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"!!!!!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">66</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token number\">23</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"2>3\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>试一试，结果跟想的不太一样……对吧</p>\n<p>emm，不如先到这里……作为一个入门……要讲的实在很多。最后一个实例，跟数据类型有很大关系，自己想一想……</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"已经下载好了python？很好……我们可以开始了！ Hello World我猜你应该还没忘掉print吧（首先，要写一段可以重复运行的python程序，需要你打开IDLE，选择Flie-&gt;New File 然后你会看到这个： OK，现在可以试着输入一些代码了…… print...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":599,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Hello-World\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Hello World</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Print\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Print()</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Tipsd","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/07/16/R7SikOfH.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"第一个博客！（大概","uid":"4c34cbeaaac838d4c6a4488d96f7f63d","slug":"新建文本文档","date":"2023-07-12T10:13:48.000Z","updated":"2023-07-16T06:46:17.095Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/新建文本文档.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/07/16/JvKwnpyr.jpg","text":"你好啊！这里是Tipsd的博客…… 现在看起来……还不怎么样……因为我也没想好要写什么……那就先把这篇当做测试(oﾟ▽ﾟ)o 感觉像QQ空间一样 起因（超大毕竟，也是别人教我搭建的博客…… ……？ 可恶，我好像没法直接换行学的半斤八两 进一步（小一点然后是……图片……(￣▽￣)／...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":330,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Tipsd","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img1.imgtp.com/2023/07/1